<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Node Demo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: darkorchid">
    <%- include('partials/nav.ejs') %>
    <h1 style="color: yellow">Contact Page</h1>
    <!-- http://127.0.0.1:2020/contact?person=praveen&gender=male&age=18&study=btech -->
    <p>
      <%= qs.person %> is <%= qs.gender %> and he is <%= qs.age %> old and he
      studies <%= qs.study %>
    </p>
    <p style="color: skyblue">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consectetur,
      accusamus illo debitis expedita molestias facilis ratione ipsa nostrum?
      Illo praesentium consectetur debitis est nihil consequuntur magnam magni
      veniam quia ea voluptatibus nisi cumque laboriosam unde aspernatur
      voluptas, quibusdam nulla delectus. Quae deleniti nemo necessitatibus
      iure, impedit a in quas, non, excepturi animi blanditiis sit velit
      praesentium nobis consequatur tenetur at quisquam accusantium sunt optio
      cupiditate soluta ipsum exercitationem? Accusamus explicabo repudiandae
